data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch on a massive corner lot. The interior features a vaulted family room with stone fireplace, open kitchen with breakfast area, laundry room off kitchen & large master bedroom! Outside youll find a perfect backyard for entertaining, gardening or kids sports. Exterior also includes a large new shop and an additional gravel parking spot for your camper, boat or trailer. Roof recently replaced with architectural shingles. Trane HVAC system has been maintained professionally every 6 months. Schedule your tour today and enjoy the gorgeous rose bushes as you will the entire home!
